# GOLDEN SPIRAL

**Action:** Color in any which way.  Watch Donald In Mathemagic Land on youtube.

![](https://i.imgur.com/4i0PDAX.png)

The Golden ratio again and again.  The figure shown is not precisely a Golden Spiral, it is made of circular arcs each of which is smaller than the previous one by the Golden Ratio.

